        "instructions": "## Task: Even or Odd\nWrite an `if/else` statement that checks if `num` is even. Print `'Even'` or `'Odd'`.",
        "starterCode": "#include <stdio.h>\n\nint main() {\n    int num = 4;\n    if (num % 2 == ___) {\n        printf(\"___\\n\");\n    } ___ {\n        printf(\"___\\n\");\n    }\n    return 0;\n}",
        "solution": "#include <stdio.h>\nint main() {\n    int num = 4;\n    if (num % 2 == 0) {\n        printf(\"Even\\n\");\n    } else {\n        printf(\"Odd\\n\");\n    }\n    return 0;\n}",
